 />\n利申 pt dc9"},{"pid":"fce49a0c1da13b711dd5486d88d9aeba089d454b","tid":342341,"uid":1312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實個錶好似顯示唔到四位數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n關顯唔顯示到咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc389a8b4dfd31d10a69025658f990dd5a26dac","tid":342341,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個網民係咪個的士狗</blockquote><br />\n似啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ba5aadaa361eb9fd4ff607ef9e88772e8f1905","tid":342341,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>機管局應該整張的士價目表掛喺的士站，由機場出發到唔同酒店幾多錢左右</blockquote><br />\n係機場的士站有架,仲有人派張卡仔寫車牌同價目表</blockquote><br />\n不過啲遊客有無細心睇果張嘢就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能以為只係抄底車牌號碼"},{"pid":"4d38bb4052e8b8423e5542a86ec57091af5e7a5d","tid":342341,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"香港幾時先有的士判官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7b9d0f724bf6713df03b248861c7ae4b844027","tid":342341,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實個錶好似顯示唔到四位數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n關顯唔顯示到咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分分鐘錶都冇落<br />\n手噤噤到個錶千七蚊噤撚到天光都未撚噤完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 搵旅行社book架豪華七人車接送都唔洗1000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55b953edb1e0c070442b4d66acbeac127f12a63","tid":342341,"uid":160