:43:00.000Z","msg":"個個屌個的士狗 唔諗下幾多香港人去外國成個背囊比人偷都係咁 <br />\n鬼佬有無幫你地d香港人鬧d垃圾搶人野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6424f06db02d00db319a063efc7d1cd2900d1162","tid":342341,"uid":70163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"最撚鐘意停係巴士站等客 <br />\n<br />\n最撚鐘意小路出大路唔讓大路行先<br />\n<br />\n最撚鐘意屈客錢 37比40唔找 96 比100又唔找<br />\n<br />\n最撚鐘意拒載 荃灣返青衣 即話轉更唔去 走左望返架車見到載左鬼佬走....<br />\n<br />\n最撚鐘意恰你唔識路 長沙灣去旺角 都可以搵條長又多車既路黎行 你老尾"},{"pid":"5ab2a5c8933e0e3051632ea3b60d4e3cc236b8dd","tid":342341,"uid":83062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:18:02.000Z","msg":"141隧道費都唔駛啦"},{"pid":"d9d1f0a51b78faf914f5e4563ad6533b0a3ff1bb","tid":342341,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:26:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的士狗=賤種職業</blockquote><br />\n本身已經係黃皮狗賤種基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b1becf7984ce1b78862355e55b42444ebb7726","tid":342341,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫稿條友竟然話真係跳錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要搭$1480的士<br />\n<br />\n起錶$24<br />\n加多7每200米$1.7，直到7公里跳到$83.5<br />\n<br />\n剩返$1396.5，扣返青馬$30<br />\n每200米$1.2<br />\n即係碌咗227.75公里（大約香港來回廣州）<br />\n<br />\n以香港車速平均80km/h<br />\n要搭3個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重有短加長減"},{"pid":"33ee8155eab786b946a968220d92f865c8b478d6","tid":342341,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"我之前去外國見過有D機場公交站棟個牌響個站牌側邊話慎防濫收定騙收額外費用之類. 唔知係當地政府負責整定點.<br />\n可參考."},{"pid":"c28e44d0e4fa306510ab25dbab236f65f3c9bdce","tid":342341,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢d野唔應該係已發展國家出現<br />\n變撚左東南亞咩dllm</blockquote><br />\nsor9ry ，菲律賓用uber好撚過你班的士狗多多聲，依家係連東南亞都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實依家香港好撚危險</blockquote><br />\n賤種基因本性係偷呃拐騙"},{"pid":"2613563b02ffaf048b3899a283510e6256e6288e","tid":342341,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:31:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個屌個的士狗 唔諗下幾多香港人去外國成個背囊比人偷都係咁 <br />\n鬼佬有無幫你地d香港人鬧d垃圾搶人野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支持巴打發起的士業齊宰客行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401ffb1fb2592be358766fc817ac12dd7584d62c","tid":342341,"uid":63164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>機場上的士唔係上車前會有張收據係預幾多錢架咩</blockquote><br />\n幾年前坐過機場的返歸<br />\n正規的直頭有張飛仔有晒車牌number</blockquote><br />\n仲會有個著曬西裝嘅人問你去邊，再帶你去指定隊道排</blockquote><br />\n我今個月係機場返屋企都有係啊<br />\n點解會屈到成千銀</blockquote><br />\n前幾日係機場坐的士都係<br />\n有哂機場人員安排，出埋張飛仔講哂d info<br />\n個兩個外國人係咪自己出去搵的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf45f09b7b7617a6b3b2dd5b18a7dd156a879fe","tid":342341,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家好多東南亞國家都有官方的士app,同uber一樣用法，穩陣又唔洗比人呃。<br />\n係香港咁衰，就算有個的士app都永遠無車同迫你加錢先有車。真係唔好怪人用uber,香港的士佬最衰格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本係黃皮膚做生意冇良心"},{"pid":"e94ddfd9d9706d97210c452e6ee3121a07afdf37","tid":342341,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"個條時光隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw咁都有連登仔死撐的士佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾時放完暑假"},{"pid"