aces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱 唔明負皮d人咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n零負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊佢個cm"},{"pid":"03ea0a716928b38f367a9cfc5831033348b1d40d","tid":342341,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次打風諗住係大學站搭返中大，收我一位90<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地三個人。當場屌柒佢，等多陣有架正價二十幾蚊返到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港打風有幾何揸車會有事吖， 你估外國咩， 班撚樣坐地起價撳住搶"},{"pid":"06dd5b0cfd58021dfdb8920ed458e3dca028510c","tid":342341,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲捉到罰幾多， 點解的士狗明知成日放蛇都照做， 罰好少？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}